<view class="safe-page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title">台球计分器</view>
    <text class="subtitle">专业的台球比赛记分工具，随时随地记录精彩瞬间</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="corner"></view>
    <view class="card-header">
      <t-icon name="thunder" size="36rpx" color="#fcbb00"></t-icon>
      <text class="card-title">开始比赛</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">选择一种比赛模式，立即开始记分</view>
    <view class="mode-list">
      <view class="mode-btn green" bindtap="goMatchBall" hover-class="green-hover">
        <view class="mode-content">
          <view class="badge">8</view>
          <text class="mode-text">去比赛</text>
        </view>
        <t-icon name="chevron-right" size="40rpx" class="arrow"></t-icon>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">功能特性</view>
    <view class="features">
      <view class="feature-card" hover-class="feature-hover">
        <view class="feat-content">
          <t-icon name="chat-double" size="40rpx" color="#2eb873"></t-icon>
          <text class="feat-title">专业规则</text>
        </view>
        <text class="feat-desc">内置标准规则与9球追分规则，支持自定义设置</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-card" hover-class="feature-hover">
        <view class="feat-content">
          <t-icon name="history" size="40rpx" color="#ff8b1a"></t-icon>
          <text class="feat-title">历史记录</text>
        </view>
        <text class="feat-desc">本地保存比赛记录，随时回顾过去战绩</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-card" hover-class="feature-hover">
        <view class="feat-content">
          <t-icon name="chart-radial" size="40rpx" color="#f5c73d"></t-icon>
          <text class="feat-title">数据统计</text>
        </view>
        <text class="feat-desc">详细的普胜、炸清、接清数据分析</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-card" hover-class="feature-hover">
        <view class="feat-content">
          <t-icon name="usergroup-add" size="40rpx" color="#6fb1ff"></t-icon>
          <text class="feat-title">多人模式</text>
        </view>
        <text class="feat-desc">支持2-3人防守技战，灵活适应不同场景</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    <t-icon name="info-circle" size="36rpx" color="#ff8b1a"></t-icon>
    <text class="notice-text">温馨提示：本应用为本地离线模式，所有比赛数据仅保存在当前设备中，清理缓存或重装程序可能会导致数据丢失。</text>
  </view>
</view>
